If you wish to have an official release of yours on your SoundCloud profile, then you can mark a Playlist as an Album, EP, Single or a Compilation. This will then show up under the Albums tab on your profile.  Just go to the Playlist’s edit page and edit the Playlist type section accordingly :    You’ll need to set a release date for your Album, hit save and then you’re good to go.
